summary: BABY APUSTAJA - Baby Apu, also known as Peepo or Helper, is a pepe-variant that is used to represent a much younger and kinder frog. Fed up with low-effort memecoins, more often than not led by deceptive developers, Baby Apu decided to create his own fairly launched, fully transparent coin on the ETH Chain: Baby Apu – the one and only token for all frens. Having already conquered the internet and the hearts of millions of people, Baby Apu is now on his way to conquer the cryptosphere. If you consider yourself a fren, feel free to join us on this amazing ride to the only place where a character like Baby Apu belongs to: the moon.
